premise_source_doc_sentence: Two actors who respectively portrayed characters in both Battle Royale and its 2003 sequel , Battle Royale II : Requiem , also appear in TOKYO 10 +01 : Masanobu Ando , who played the character Kazuo Kiriyama in Battle Royale , and Natsuki Kato , who played the character Saki Sakurai in Battle Royale II .

PlayStation All-Stars Battle Royale is a crossover fighting video game developed by SuperBot Entertainment , in conjunction with SCE Santa Monica Studio , and published by Sony Computer Entertainment for the PlayStation 3 and PlayStation Vita video game consoles .
Kitano  (  Battle Royale  )  , a Battle Royale character
The novel was translated into English by Yuji Oniki and published by Viz Media in 2003 .
